title: My device connected to E5377Bs-508’s wireless network, but cannot open Web UI
answer:
A: 

 1. Double  to check![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=39254) your wireless network connection on windows start bar. Make sure your device is connected with your E5377Bs-508 not other Wi-Fi device. 

 2. Open Web Browser from your device (ex. Microsoft Internet Explorer). Go *<u>http://192.168.8.1</u>* to open E5377Bs-508’s Web UI.
